extends layout

block content
    h2(class='py-2') ClubGG
    p
        | A variety of micro, small, and mid stakes cash games are running in 
        a(href='https://play.clubgg.net/dlink/7KAFf6m2TgiDbFif8') The Card Room 
        | club on ClubGG.  The currency in this club is ADA, giving 
        | utility to your crypto currency!!  To get started, see below.
    h4(class='py-2') On-board
    ol(style='color: white;')
        li Download the application at 
            a(href='https://www.clubgg.net/') clubgg.net
        li Search for club ID 
            b 434282 
            | and join.
        li Set your ClubGG nickname to match an $adahandle in your Cardano wallet.  
            | Cash-in and cash-out will be done using this wallet and handle.
        li Request chips in ClubGG and send the same amount of ADA to 
            a(href='https://pool.pm/$tcr.clubgg') $tcr.clubgg
        li Notify SuperKK#5404 in Discord with the transaction ID.  After the transaction 
            | is verified, the chip request will be approved.
        li Play poker (see games below)
        li Cash-out may be requested at any time.  To cash-out, contact SuperKK#5404 in 
            | Discord.  After verifying your chip count and $adahandle, the request will 
            | be approved and transaction sent.  Please note that a small amount may be 
            | deducted to cover network gas fees (~0.2 ADA).
        li Join 
            a(href='https://discord.com/invite/WETf8Y9wF3') The Card Room 
            | on Discord and follow the channel #clubgg to stay up to date with games,
            | players and everything else related to poker.  Notify KK when you join 
            | to be assigned the @CLUBGG role.

